text: ( Source : Kaplan Inc ) Dr. Betty Vandenbosch Named President of Kaplan University CHICAGO, Illinois -- ( October 13 , 2015 ) -- Kaplan University's Board of Trustees is pleased to announce that Dr. Betty Vandenbosch has been appointed President
